<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="despair-n">despair <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'speə(r)/    美 /dɪ'sper/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>绝望：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>drive / throw a person to despair 
使某人陷于绝望</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>to the despair of sb</strong> 
使某人绝望的是</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He has never fallen into despair. 
他从不悲观失望。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-despair">in despair</h3>
<p>1.<strong>绝望地：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Lance put his head on the doctor’s desk in despair.  
兰斯绝望地趴在医生的桌子上。</p><footer>北师大⑦ – 21</footer></div></div>